dnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girlfriends%20pay%20me%20to%20conduct%20loyalty%20tests%20via%20Instagram%20DMs.%20It's%20a%20lucrative%20gig%2C%20and%20most%20boyfriends%20fail.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20featuring%20selfies%20of%20Trinity%20Howard%20and%20screenshots%20of%20DM%20conversations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f641020abc1efe8fce6b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrinity%20Howard%20conducts%20loyalty%20tests%20through%20Lazo.%3Cp%3ETrinity%20Howard%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrinity%20Howard's%20personal%20experience%20with%20a%20cheating%20boyfriend%20inspired%20her%20to%20help%20other%20girls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20now%20a%20loyalty%20tester%20for%20Lazo%2C%20charging%20%2470%20per%20mission%20to%20see%20if%20a%20boyfriend%20will%20cheat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHoward%20conducts%2015-20%20loyalty%20tests%20a%20week%20and%20says%2090%25%20of%20the%20men%20who%20respond%20to%20her%20fail%20the%20test.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Trinity%20Howard%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20loyalty%20tester%20in%20Tampa.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20became%20a%20loyalty%20tester%2C%20I%20had%20my%20own%20run-in%20with%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20a%20toxic%20relationship%20for%20two%20years%20during%20high%20school.%20Despite%20my%20commitment%20to%20loyalty%2C%20my%20first%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreakup-cheating-self-worth-lesson-husband-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20cheater%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20our%20relationship%2C%20I%20always%20knew%20he%20had%20another%20girl%20on%20the%20side.%20I%20often%20saw%20them%20sitting%20together%20at%20lunch%20or%20talking%20at%20school%2C%20but%20when%20I%20confronted%20him%2C%20he%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20end%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20block%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20he%20never%20meant%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20test%20his%20loyalty%20and%20texted%20him%20using%20a%20fake%20number%2C%20posing%20as%20the%20other%20girl.%20When%20he%20wanted%20to%20meet%20up%20with%20her%2C%20I%20agreed%20to%20that%2C%20too.%20I%20grabbed%20his%20things%20from%20my%20house%2C%20and%20at%202%20a.m.%2C%20I%20showed%20up%20as%20her.%20We%20broke%20up%20that%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20it%20then%2C%20but%20that%20was%20my%20first%20loyalty%20test%2C%20and%20it's%20now%20my%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a28af62-a51b-4d68-aea7-e91c69b34dc4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20a%20loyalty%20tester%20for%20others%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20long%20after%20I%20caught%20my%20own%20boyfriend%2C%20I%20made%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40trinitykayh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20sharing%20my%20story%2C%20and%20it%20quickly%20blew%20up.%20I%20woke%20up%20with%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20followers%20on%20TikTok%2C%20mainly%20girls%20wanting%20me%20to%20test%20their%20boyfriends.%20I%20realized%20this%20could%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20help%20others%20who've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmove-on-cheating-affair-relationship-breakup-therapist-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperienced%20the%20same%20hurt%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20my%20new%20following%20to%20DM%20me%20if%20they%20were%20interested%20in%20a%20loyalty%20test%20and%20that%20I'd%20do%20it%20free%20of%20charge.%20As%20more%20women%20took%20me%20up%20on%20my%20offer%2C%20my%20new%20gig%20started%20to%20take%20up%20more%20and%20more%20of%20my%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20in%20school%2C%20had%20homework%2C%20played%20softball%2C%20and%20worked%20out%20%E2%80%94%20it%20became%20very%20hard%20to%20juggle%20everything%2C%20so%20I%20began%20to%20request%20donations.%20I%20told%20my%20audience%20that%20I'd%20make%20those%20who%20offered%20a%20donation%20of%20their%20choosing%20my%20priority.%20Some%20donated%20%245.00%2C%20and%20some%20even%20donated%20%2450.00.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20I%20started%20requesting%20donations%2C%20there%20were%20still%20thousands%20of%20women%20messaging%20me%20for%20my%20help.%20It%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bfefe91a-90a1-4b65-a8af-60f4ea0005dd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20a%20loyalty%20tester%20on%20Lazo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20Lazo%2C%20a%20platform%20specializing%20in%20relationship%20loyalty%20tests%2C%20contacted%20me.%20They%20found%20me%20on%20TikTok%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20would%20offer%20my%20service%20through%20their%20platform.%20I%20agreed.%20Now%2C%20I%20do%20loyalty%20tests%20for%20a%20living%20and%20help%20even%20more%20women%20than%20when%20I%20did%20it%20on%20my%20own.%20I%20mostly%20test%20boyfriends%20but%20have%20tested%20about%20five%20husbands%20since%20I%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20users%20come%20to%20Lazo%20needing%20a%20loyalty%20test%2C%20they%20can%20pick%20the%20'tester'%20they%20want%20based%20on%20location%2C%20hobbies%2C%20interests%2C%20hair%20color%2C%20and%20other%20things%20they%20think%20their%20significant%20other%20might%20be%20into.%20There%20are%20roughly%20400%20testers%20on%20the%20platform.%20Loyalty%20testers%20have%20different%20prices%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20price%20they%20set%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20set%20fee%20of%20%2470%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bmission.%26quot%3B%20Lazo%20takes%20%2421%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20%2449.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20how%20many%20I%20can%20handle%2C%20I%20do%2015%20to%2020%20missions%20a%20week.%20Sometimes%2C%20a%20mission%20can%20take%20a%20little%20over%20an%20hour%2C%20but%20others%20can%20take%20up%20to%20a%20week%20if%20not%20more.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20girls%20who%20come%20to%20Lazo%20are%20usually%20right%20about%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmoothie-receipt-tipped-woman-off-to-cheating-boyfriend-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeating%20boyfriends%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a214b55e-c0f1-421c-a50c-87d78a6071c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOnce%20I%20take%20on%20a%20mission%2C%20I%20get%20to%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20hiring%20me%2C%20users%20tell%20me%20what%20social%20media%20platform%20their%20boyfriend%20is%20on%2C%20where%20he%20lives%2C%20and%20what%20he%20likes.%20They'll%20tell%20me%20if%20he%20likes%20a%20flirty%20girl%20or%20if%20I%20need%20to%20take%20it%20slower%20and%20get%20to%20know%20him%20first.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20I%20can%20accept%20or%20decline%20the%20mission.%20I've%20declined%20around%2030%20missions%20because%20they%20were%20under%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20send%20a%20request%20to%20follow%20the%20boyfriend%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20if%20the%20boyfriend%20accepts%20my%20request%2C%20I'll%20DM%20him%2C%20using%20my%20first%20name%20and%20middle%20initial%2C%20and%20a%20photo%20of%20me.%20If%20the%20guy%20responds%20to%20me%20and%20interacts%20with%20my%20message%2C%2090%25%20of%20the%20time%2C%20they%20will%20fail%20the%20mission.%20Though%20many%20also%20do%20tell%20me%20they%20have%20a%20girlfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20screenshot%20of%20Instagram%20messages%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665a00e21cd3b17790422197%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222208%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Lazo%20mission.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Trinity%20Howard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ff