%3D%5C%22The%20Line%20Neom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6048e9099942cf001865d894%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22801%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Line%26quot%3B%20at%20Neom%2C%20a%20string%20of%20cities%20connected%20by%20an%20underground%20transport%20system.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20traditional%20layouts%2C%20the%20benefits%20of%20linear%20cities%20include%20efficient%20public%20transport%2C%20ready%20access%20to%20nature%2C%20and%20a%20more%20egalitarian%20lifestyle.%20Theoretically%20endless%2C%20they%20can%20easily%20extend%20as%20populations%20expand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProposals%20for%20The%20Line%20echo%20many%20of%20these%20promises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project's%20website%20presents%20the%20city%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20mass%20urbanization%20and%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20depicting%20it%20as%20a%20sustainable%20carless%20utopia%20that%20will%20preserve%2095%25%20of%20the%20region's%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeom's%20designers%20claim%20that%20all%20essential%20services%20will%20be%20accessible%20within%20five%20minutes%2C%20and%20nature%20will%20be%20just%20a%20two-minute%20walk%20away.%20AI-powered%20technology%20throughout%20the%20city%20will%20enhance%20sustainability%20and%20maximize%20residents'%20life%20expectancy%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20right%20shape%20for%20a%20city%20%E2%80%94%20they%20typically%20evolve%20over%20time%2C%20based%20on%20natural%2C%20cultural%2C%20transportation%2C%20political%2C%20and%20economic%20factors%2C%26quot%3B%20Mona%20Lovgreen%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20Canadian%20architecture%20firm%20DIALOG%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20that%20if%20designed%20correctly%2C%20The%20Line's%20linear%20form%20would%20make%20it%20accessible%20and%20facilitate%20the%20integration%20of%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20along%20its%20entire%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%2