d%20and%20prescriptive%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovgreen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Line%20is%20formed%20of%20modules%20that%20can%20each%20house%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20able%20to%20move%20about%20through%20a%20horizontal%20and%20vertical%20transport%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Line%2C%20NEOM%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64353ff22588f70018ce4071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20publicity%20image%20shows%20a%20design%20for%20'The%20Line'%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20planned%20Saudi%20Arabian%20desert%20megacity%20in%20NEOM.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompared%20to%20other%20urban%20designs%20like%20grid%20layout%2C%20radial%20layout%2C%20ring%20layout%2C%20or%20some%20combination%20of%20these%2C%20human%20experience%20in%20a%20strictly%20linear%20urban%20development%20can%20lack%20interest%20and%20variation%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Adhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20could%20become%20too%20far%20and%20segregated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20repetition%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20kit-of%20parts%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bbland%20and%20monotonous%2C%26quot%3B%20lacking%20the%20unique%20character%20that%20other%20cities%20offer%2C%20said%20Lovgreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20the%20psychological%20impact%20of%20living%20in%20such%20a%20regimented%20environment%20may%20affect%20residents'%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20structure%20is%20not%20only%20monotonous%2C%20but%20can%20limit%20social%20cohesion%2C%20according%20to%20John%20Gold%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20Urban%20Historical%20Geography%20at%20Oxford%20Brookes%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLinear%20cities%20are%20an%20extreme%20form%20of%20urban%20dispersal%20%E2%80%94%20community%20development%20and%20social%20cohesion%20still%20need%20centrality%2C%26quot%3B%20Gold%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20challenge%20in%20Neom's%20design%20is%20its%20over-reliance%20on%20technology%20and%20the%20public%20transport%20system%2C%20experts%20said.%20If%20something%20went%20wrong%2C%20the%20entire%20system%20would%20crumble%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20cities%20have%20network%20redundancy%2C%20where%20multiple%20options%20are%20available%20if%20a%20specific%20connection%20or%20intersection%20is%20blocked.%20A%20linear%20city%20may%20not%20have%20this%20capability%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Lovgreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NEOM%20Saudi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f61d46b323fc4001e0d6808%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20site%20of%20NEOM%20in%20Tabuk%20Province%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cp%3ENEOM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20The%20Line's%20proclamations%20of%20sustainability%2C%20its%20huge%20mirrored%20walls%20could%20be%20harmful%20ecologically%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20unnecessary%20heat%20gain%20within%20the%20structure%20as%20well%20as%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneom-the-line-mirrored-tower-birds-kill-saudi-arabia-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetrimental%20for%20the%20migratory%20flight%20paths%20of%20billions%20of%20birds%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20big%20issue%2C%20according%20to%20Gold%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bwho%20would%20actually%20want%20to%20live%20in%20such%20a%20'city'%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20schemes%2C%20and%20the%20Saudi%20one%20is%20a%20classic%20example%2C%20map%20out%20a%20hi-tech%20utopian%20future%20but%20never%20engage%20with%20people%20as%20they%20really%20are.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20linear%20city%20schemes%20are%20best%20left%20as%20design%20exercises%20for%20third-year