ws%20and%20watch%20them%20on%20the%20actual%20seatback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFor%20WiFi%2C%20Delta%20had%20an%20entirely%20free%20option%20available%20to%20SkyMiles%20members.%20American's%20complimentary%20option%20was%20only%2020%20minutes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20AA.com%20website%20with%20T-Mobile%20offer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6659d257d0b8e1c832caaf51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreenshot%20of%20American's%20free%20WiFi%20option%20on%20the%20author's%20iPhone.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20offers%20free%20and%20paid%20inflight%20WiFi%20options%20on%20more%20than%20650%20domestic%20narrowbody%20planes%2C%20including%20free%20sessions%20to%20SkyMiles%20members%20and%20eligible%20T-Mobile%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20also%20offers%20the%20T-Mobile%20option%20and%20a%20new%20complimentary%20one%2C%20though%20the%20latter%20is%20ad-based%20and%20only%20for%20a%20short%20duration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20is%20likely%20to%20show%20people%20what%20the%20WiFi%20is%20like%20and%20entice%20them%20to%20buy%20a%20flight%20pass%2C%20but%20the%20up-to-%2420%20price%20for%20internet%20on%20my%20American%20flight%20may%20be%20a%20little%20steep%20for%20some%20travelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHowever%2C%20my%20T-Mobile%20phone%20number%20gives%20me%20free%20and%20unlimited%20WiFi%20on%20both%20airlines.%20It's%20typically%20fast%20and%20reliable%20regardless%20of%20carrier.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20AA.com%20website%20with%20T-Mobile%20offer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6659d29f1cd3b177904202de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20T-Mobile%20service%20extends%20to%20Alaska%20Airlines%20and%20United%20Airlines%2C%20too.%20In%20almost%20every%20case%2C%20I've%20had%20working%20WiFi%20for%20most%20of%20the%20flight.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican's%20WiFi%20was%20more%20reliable%20on%20this%20roundtrip%20journey%2C%20with%20Delta's%20cutting%20out%20on%20two%20separate%20occasions%20for%20about%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20fair%2C%20internet%20connectivity%20on%20planes%20is%20always%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20choppy%20due%20to%20uncontrollable%20factors%20like%20weather%2C%20and%20I've%20had%20the%20WiFi%20cut%20on%20American%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20solution%20is%20to%20just%20try%20to%20avoid%20working%20on%20things%20that%20require%20the%20internet%20when%20I'm%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConsidering%20I%20use%20T-Mobile%20WiFi%20and%20always%20bring%20my%20tablet%20to%20watch%20shows%2C%20neither%20of%20the%20airlines'%20internet%20nor%20IFE%20setups%20is%20a%20dealbreaker%20for%20me.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Diet%20Coke%20and%20Biscoff%20cookies%20on%20the%20tray%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664b940814fb5b23cc5e5d8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222637%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20snack%20and%20drink%20I%20got%20on%20my%20American%20flight.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20T-Mobile%20phone%20number%2C%20Kindle%20Fire%2C%20and%20charging%20cables%2C%20I%20can%20work%20or%20be%20entertained%20regardless%20of%20whether%20I%20fly%20American%20or%20Delta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20prefer%20American's%20IFE%20setup%2C%20but%20its%20economy%20comfort%20is%20so%20comparable%20to%20Delta's%20that%20I%20care%20more%20about%20price%20and%20timing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223323%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20seat%20on%20Delta's%20A220.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%