ption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGrowing%20up%2C%20I%20always%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20mom.%20I%20wasn't%20as%20sure%20about%20getting%20married.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20did%20get%20married%2C%20and%20though%20I%20love%20my%20husband%2C%20I%20sometimes%20don't%20enjoy%20being%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20I%20always%20love%20being%20a%20mom%20to%20my%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20when%20I%20was%20a%20young%20girl%2C%20marriage%20didn't%20seem%20all%20that%20appealing%20to%20me.%20The%20idea%20of%20being%20with%20someone%20forever%20and%20having%20to%20share%20a%20space%2C%20finances%2C%20and%20everything%20else%20just%20seemed%20a%20bit%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20liked%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20a%20serious%20relationship%20while%20keeping%20two%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgirlfriend-boyfriend-living-together-have-separate-bedrooms-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseparate%20living%20spaces%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20liked%20my%20space%20and%20time%20to%20myself%20and%20wanted%20it%20to%20stay%20that%20way.%20But%20I%20also%20knew%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20mother%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20mother%20more%20than%20anything%20in%20the%20world.%20Being%20a%20mother%20was%20always%20much%20more%20important%20to%20me%20than%20becoming%20a%20wife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20things%20change%20in%20life%2C%20and%20eventually%2C%20I%20decided%20marriage%20was%20right%20for%20me.%20I%20met%20my%20now%20husband%2C%20a%20handsome%20bohemian%20Italian%20artist%2C%20during%20my%20first%20summer%20living%20in%20Italy%20almost%2010%20years%20ago.%20We%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20and%20after%20a%20year%20of%20dating%2C%20we%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-in-together-relationship-dynamic-change-2024-4%5C%22%20target