ense%20to%20me%20to%20be%20married%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20be%20married%20to%20the%20father%20of%20my%20babies%20%E2%80%94%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20married%20first%2C%20and%20then%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Ehave%20children.%20It%20was%20almost%20a%20shocking%20revelation%20to%20myself%2C%20since%20I%20never%20thought%20it%20mattered%20to%20me.%20It%20turned%20out%2C%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%2C%20it%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20and%20white%20photo%20of%20Caroline%20Chirichella%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20daughter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665a07c21cd3b177904227bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222083%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Chirichella%20feels%20as%20though%20she%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20mother.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Caroline%20Chirichella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274ba7833-2f18-4bcc-88dc-452a50d7ff29%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20always%20enjoy%20everything%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20a%20'wife'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20been%20together%20going%20on%2010%20years%2C%20and%20have%20been%20married%20for%20a%20little%20over%20seven.%20It's%20strange%2C%20but%20sometimes%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwant-be-tradwife-traditional-wife-marriage-homemaker-life-meaning-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elove%20being%20a%20wife%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20having%20that%20title.%20I%20actually%20like%20cleaning%20the%20house%20and%20making%20meals%20specially%20for%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20are%20times%20that%20I%20really%20don't%20enjo