C%20and%20so%20is%20PM%20Modi!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20screenshots%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20Maldives%20bookings%20available%20on%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20prompting%20questions%20about%20whether%20the%20company%20had%20reversed%20its%20boycott.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENishant%20Pitti%20clarified%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20boycott%20remains%20in%20place%20and%20any%20future%20changes%20would%20be%20formally%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEaseMyTrip%20initially%20halted%20operations%20in%20Maldives%20in%20January%20after%20three%20Maldivian%20ministers%20made%20derogatory%20comments%20about%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20following%20his%20visit%20to%20Lakshadweep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20flight%20bookings%20to%20the%20Maldives%2C%20made%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20government%2C%20impacted%20240%2C000%20annual%20bookings%20through%20their%20platform.%20Prashant%20Pitti%2C%20co-founder%20of%20EaseMyTrip%2C%20noted%20a%20significant%2040%20per%20cent%20surge%20in%20bookings%20last%20year%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20boycott%2C%20EaseMyTrip%20recently%20reported%20its%20highest-ever%20earnings%20before%20interest%2C%20taxes%2C%20depreciation%2C%20and%20amortization%20(EBITDA)%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20amounting%20to%20Rs%202%2C282%20million%2C%20reflecting%20a%2019%20percent%20year-on-year%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20consolidated%20revenue%20from%20operations%20for%20the%20same%20period%20reached%20Rs%205%2C906%20million%2C%20marking%20a%2032%20percent%20increase%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%20FY24%2C%20EaseMyTrip%20demonstrated%20impressive%20growth%20across%20various%20segments%2C%20with%201.4%20lakh%20hotel%20night%20bookings%2C%20representing%20a%2039%20percent%20increase%20over%20the%20previous%20year%20and%20contributing%2012%20percent%20to%20the%20s