20and%20its%20allies%20to%20win%20between%20350%20and%20400%20seats.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20alliance%20won%20352.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suggested%20size%20of%20the%20majority%20would%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20continue%20unabated%20with%20its%20current%20policy%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gary%20Dugan%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Dalma%20Capital%20Management%20Ltd.%20in%20Dubai.%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20imagine%20a%203-5%25%20return%20from%20the%20market%20on%20Monday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjp-may-sweep-polls-but-fall-short-of-370-seat-target-predict-bookies-5798090%5C%22%3EWill%20BJP%20Cross%20370%20Seats%3F%20What%20Bookies%20In%20Shadow%20Betting%20Market%20Expect%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20the%20results%20on%20June%204%20align%20with%20the%20exit%20polls%2C%20analysts%20expect%20the%20NSE%20Nifty%2050%20Index%20to%20reach%20a%20new%20record.%20The%20main%20gauge%20slid%20nearly%202%25%20to%2022%2C531%20last%20week%20as%20foreign%20investors%20treaded%20cautiously%20ahead%20of%20the%20election%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeign%20investors%20will%20need%20to%20cover%20short%20positions%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Abhay%20Agarwal%2C%20founder%20and%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20Piper%20Serica%20Advisors.%20%26quot%3BMargin%20calls%20on%20short%20positions%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20market%20spiking%20beyond%2023%2C000%20on%20Monday%20-%20a%20new%20high%20-%20and%20close%20to%2023%2C500%20on%20June%204th%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20numbers%20for%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20are%20above%20350%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20state-owned%20companies%2C%20infrastructure-linked%20firms%20and%20those%20of%20some%20corporates%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20conglomerate%20may%20be%20in%20focus%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%