o%2C%20partner%20and%20portfolio%20manager)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20we%20see%20a%20renewed%20push%20to%20implement%20long-stymied%20but%20potentially%20economically%20transformative%20reforms%20to%20politically-sensitive%20areas%20such%20as%20agriculture%2C%20labor%20laws%2C%20and%20land%20acquisition%2C%20there%20would%20be%20potential%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BIndia%20premium%26quot%3B%20to%20other%20emerging%20markets%20to%20widen%20even%20further%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%2C%20however%2C%20that%20political%20capital%20ends%20up%20focused%20more%20on%20potentially%20divisive%20social%20issues%2C%20I'd%20expect%20the%20opposite%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuantum%20Advisors%20(Nilesh%20Shetty%2C%20portfolio%20manager)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20consensus%20view%20was%20that%20PM%20Modi%20would%20come%20back%20and%20exit%20polls%20reaffirm%20that%20view.%20Any%20opportunistic%20shorts%20will%20cover%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20near-term%20rally%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOver%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%20election%20results%20have%20not%20mattered%20much%20as%20average%20GDP%20growth%20has%20hovered%20around%206.5%25%20irrespective%20of%20the%20government%20in%20power%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrust%20Mutual%20Fund%20(Sandeep%20Bagla%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEquity%2C%20currency%2C%20and%20bond%20markets%20should%20greet%20the%20exit%20poll%20results%20with%20a%20renewed%20enthusiasm%20as%20the%20uncertainty%20regarding%20poll%20verdict%20is%20finally%20getting%20over%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20likely%20buoyancy%20in%20the%20rupee%2C%20bonds%20should%20be%20well%20supported%20and%20there's%20a%20distinct%20possibility%20that%20the%2010-year%20benchmark%20bond%20yield%20could%20touch%206.90%25%20in%20the%20near%20future%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESociete%20Generale%20SA%20(Rajat