te%20from%20the%20Air%20Force%20in%20the%20next%20story.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20next%20slide%2C%20the%20actor%20added%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20report%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20AFP.%20Mr%20Evan%20has%20highlighted%20the%20quote%20by%20an%20Air%20Force%20spokesperson.%20It%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20object%20Chris%20Evans%20is%20signing%20in%20the%20USO%20tour%20photo%20from%202016%20is%20an%20explosive%20ordnance%20disposal%20(EOD)%20inert%20training%20aid.%20The%20object%20is%20meant%20to%20model%20an%20artillery%20shell%20and%20is%20for%20display%20and%20training%20purposes%20only.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMr%20Evan's%20Instagram%20Stories%20were%20later%20shared%20by%20a%20user%20on%20Reddit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3EPosts%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FFauxmoi%2Fcomments%2F1d4kg6r%2Fchris_evans_clears_up_false_rumors_about_him%2F%5C%22%3Efauxmoi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cncommunity%20on%20Reddit%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20picture%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frafah-strike-israel-gaza-nikki-haley-writes-finish-them-on-israeli-bombs-days-after-rafah-strike-5768519%5C%22%3Eformer%20US%20presidential%20hopeful%20Nikki%20Haley%3C%2Fa%3E%20writing%20%E2%80%9CFinish%20Them%E2%80%9D%20on%20an%20Israeli%20shell%20surfaced%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20pic%20was%20shared%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frafah-strike-israel-gaza-nikki-haley-writes-finish-them-on-israeli-bombs-days-after-rafah-strike-5768519%5C%22%3Eformer%20UN%20Ambassador%20Danny%20Danon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20accompanying%20Ms%20Haley%20on%20her%20visit%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20May%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22lt