ealth%2C%20you%20may%20have%20been%20misled%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20class%20action%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrebiotics%20are%20a%20special%20type%20of%20fiber%20that%20can%20act%20as%20food%20for%20healthy%20bacteria%20in%20your%20gut%2C%26quot%3B%20Poppi's%20website%20claims%20of%20its%20products.%20%26quot%3BEach%20can%20of%20poppi%20includes%20agave%20inulin%2C%20a%20prebiotic%20(and%20natural%20sweetener!)%20extracted%20from%20the%20agave%20tequilana%20plant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24718488-poppi-soda-class-action-complaint%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20Wednesday%2C%20alleges%20the%20low-sugar%2C%20%26quot%3Bgut-healthy%26quot%3B%20sodas%20contain%20such%20small%20amounts%20of%20prebiotic%20fiber%20(just%202%20grams%20per%20serving)%20that%20the%20average%20consumer%20wouldn't%20experience%20any%20health%20benefits%20from%20drinking%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20consumer%20would%20need%20to%20drink%20more%20than%20four%20Poppi%20sodas%20in%20a%20day%20to%20realize%20any%20potential%20health%20benefits%20from%20its%20prebiotic%20fiber%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%2C%20which%20seeks%20%245%2C000%2C000%20in%20financial%20damages%2C%20says.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20even%20if%20a%20consumer%20were%20to%20do%20this%2C%20Poppi's%20high%20sugar%20content%20would%20offset%20most%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20of%20these%20purported%20gut%20health%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20goes%20on%20to%20say%20that%20an%20inulin-based%20diet%20could%20cause%20%26quot%3Binflammation%20and%20even%20liver%20damage%26quot%3B%20with%20doses%20as%20low%20as%2010%20grams%20per%20day%20and%20demands%20a%20jury%20trial%20to%20determine%20whether%20Poppi%20has%20broken%20the%20law%20with%20its%20advertisements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPoppi's%20sodas%2C%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20in%20the%20years%20since%20their%202018%20a